    <item>
      <title>华尔街冷静的市场中风险偏好再度飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/risk-appetites-roaring-anew-in-wall-street-s-unflappable-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[要了解目前风险资产的投机狂热，请看一下周五的交易情况。尽管全球最大的债券市场因热门经济数据而再次陷入低迷，但众多投资专业人士仍被一位 meme-stock 大师直播其在 GameStop Corp. 持有的近 3 亿美元股票所吸引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/risk-appetites-roaring-anew-in-wall-street-s-unflappable-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 20:37:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着公司调查违规行为，Snowflake 正在努力加强安全控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/snowflake-working-to-beef-up-controls-as-firms-probe-breaches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Advanced Auto Parts Inc. 和 Live Nation Entertainment Inc. 等公司正在调查潜在的数据泄露事件之际，Snowflake Inc. 正试图让其客户实施更严格的安全控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/snowflake-working-to-beef-up-controls-as-firms-probe-breaches</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 20:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Thoma Bravo 考虑通过私人债务融资 35 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/thoma-bravo-considers-private-debt-for-3-5-billion-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Thoma Bravo 已与私人信贷机构取得联系，寻求为其自动化专业服务提供商 ConnectWise 筹集约 35 亿美元的新融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/thoma-bravo-considers-private-debt-for-3-5-billion-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 20:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社交媒体巨头回避学区对成瘾问题的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/social-media-giants-avoid-school-districts-addiction-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 和其他社交媒体公司在数百起由学区提起的诉讼中驳回了新的索赔，这些诉讼旨在收回解决学生使用社交媒体所造成的负面影响的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/social-media-giants-avoid-school-districts-addiction-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 19:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软在强烈抗议后加强了 Windows AI 工具的安全性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/microsoft-beefs-up-security-of-windows-ai-tool-after-outcry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司表示，即将推出的一系列人工智能品牌 PC 的一项关键新功能将以“关闭”状态发货，此前网络安全专家表示，该工具为黑客创造了一个诱人的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/microsoft-beefs-up-security-of-windows-ai-tool-after-outcry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 17:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌在美国反垄断案中支付 230 万美元由法官而非陪审团审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/google-pays-us-2-3-million-for-antitrust-trial-before-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官裁定，在美国司法部的反垄断案中，Alphabet Inc. 将接受法庭审判，而不是陪审团审判，该案指控该公司在向联邦政府支付 230 万美元后垄断了广告技术市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/google-pays-us-2-3-million-for-antitrust-trial-before-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:21:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着人工智能赌注的消退，德克萨斯电力公司 Vistra 遭遇三年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/texas-power-firm-vistra-vst-eyes-worst-week-in-three-years-as-ai-bets-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员放弃了对人工智能推动电力需求激增的押注，电力生产商 Vistra Corp. 的股价创下了自 2021 年 2 月以来最糟糕的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/texas-power-firm-vistra-vst-eyes-worst-week-in-three-years-as-ai-bets-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉尔重返 YouTube，GameStop 股价因股票出售计划而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/gamestop-s-gme-11-billion-rally-depends-on-roaring-kitty-s-youtube-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，备受期待的基思·吉尔 (Keith Gill) 重返 YouTube，加之这家视频游戏零售商意外公布了收益报告并宣布计划在当天早些时候出售最多 7500 万股增发股票，GameStop Corp. 的股价随后进一步下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/gamestop-s-gme-11-billion-rally-depends-on-roaring-kitty-s-youtube-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:46:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
